The Prince has come under fire over his friendship with convicted pedophile Jeffrey Epstein, who has been accused in court documents of supplying the royal with an underage girl.

Buckingham Palace has issued a statement strongly denying the allegations, which Ms Ferguson, 55, repeated during an interview with NBC News.

'I won't stand by - because I know what it feels like to have salacious lies made up about you - and not support him so publicly,' she told Matt Lauer.

